    {
      "text": "Toy Story Racer is a 2001 kart racing game developed by Traveller's Tales and Tiertex Design Studios and published by Activision. It was based on the Toy Story franchise, primarily the first film. The game was released in March 2001 for the Game Boy Color and PlayStation systems. The PlayStation version received \"generally favorable reviews\" according to Metacritic. In 2010, the PlayStation version was re-released on the PlayStation Store as a PS one Classic.",
